Hi,

Was the bus running before you replaced the cold start valve?

I would recommend you review all the vacuum connections, perhaps you 
dislodged something during the repair.

Richard Atwell has an excellent FI vacuum reference online at:
http://homepage.mac.com/ratwell/VacuumHoses.html

